originalText.text:
After first week of moving in everything is going well. The leasing company was able to secure our room a month prior to our move in date which was helpful for preparation, and also provided a $1000 Amex gift card to aid in expenses. There is also a mini storage room (and helper) for packages that are delivered, which prevents packages from being stolen, with 2 entrance locks during the night (1 entrance lock during the day). We love our room as it receives a lot of sunlight (no building right in front of the window) and is spacious compared to nearby apartments for the same price.

Will update if any issue arises.
